```

#### Backend Infrastructure
```sql
-- Core Database Schema (Supabase)

-- Imported Content Storage
CREATE TABLE imported_items (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  title TEXT NOT NULL,
  content TEXT NOT NULL,
  category TEXT CHECK (category IN ('character', 'plot', 'research', 'chapter')),
  file_name TEXT,
  file_size INTEGER,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Tagging System
CREATE TABLE item_tags (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  item_id UUID REFERENCES imported_items(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  tag_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Canvas Integration
CREATE TABLE canvas_items (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  item_id UUID REFERENCES imported_items(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  position_x REAL NOT NULL,
  position_y REAL NOT NULL,
  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
);
```

### User Experience Flow

#### Import Workflow
1. **Access Library** ‚Üí Click "Library" in sidebar navigation
2. **Initiate Import** ‚Üí Click "Import Content" button
3. **File Selection** ‚Üí Drag & drop or browse for .docx/.txt files
4. **Content Processing** ‚Üí System extracts and analyzes content
5. **Category Assignment** ‚Üí Review auto-suggested categories
6. **Tag Addition** ‚Üí Add custom tags for organization
7. **Final Import** ‚Üí Click "Import to Library" to save

#### Canvas Workflow
1. **Browse Library** ‚Üí View all imported content with search/filter
2. **Select Content** ‚Üí Choose items to visualize
3. **Add to Canvas** ‚Üí Click "Add to Canvas" for each item
4. **Visual Organization** ‚Üí Drag nodes and create connections
5. **Save Layout** ‚Üí Positions automatically persist

### Success Metrics

#### User Engagement
- **Import completion rate:** % of users who complete file import
- **Library usage:** Average time spent in library per session
- **Canvas adoption:** % of imported items added to canvas
- **Content organization:** Average tags per imported item

#### Technical Performance
- **Import speed:** Time to process and categorize files
- **Search response time:** Library search performance
- **Canvas performance:** Smooth rendering with 50+ nodes
- **Error rates:** File processing failure rates

#### Business Metrics
- **User retention:** DAU/WAU ratios
- **Content volume:** Average imported items per user
- **Feature adoption:** Usage of different content categories
- **User satisfaction:** Qualitative feedback scores

